<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="ar" dir="rtl"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><title>System Control</title><link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/style.css"></head><body><div class="content"><h1>System Control - Owner Only</h1><div class="glass card"><p>حالة الإرسال: <strong><%= sendQueueState.isRunning ? (sendQueueState.isPaused ? 'متوقف مؤقتاً' : 'جارٍ الإرسال') : 'متوقف' %></strong></p><p>تمت المعالجة: <strong><%= sendQueueState.processed %> / <%= sendQueueState.total %></strong></p><p>نجاح: <strong><%= sendQueueState.success %></strong></p><p>فشل: <strong><%= sendQueueState.failed %></strong></p><p>الاشتراك: <strong><%= ownerSetup.subscriptionActive ? 'نشط' : 'غير نشط' %></strong></p><p>السيرفر المتحقق: <strong><%= ownerSetup.verifiedGuildId || '-' %></strong></p></div><div class="glass card"><h2>آخر السجل</h2><div class="table"><div class="thead logs-head"><span>الوقت</span><span>النوع</span><span>من</span><span>التفاصيل</span></div><% logs.forEach(log=>{ %><div class="trow logs-row"><span><%= new Date(log.time).toLocaleString('de-DE') %></span><span><%= log.type %></span><span><%= log.actorEmail || '-' %></span><span><%= log.message || log.plainTextPreview || '-' %></span></div><% }) %></div></div></div></body></html>